2.title: About Archangel Michael

episode of.title: How to become clairvoyant and reach God-consciousness (TV Series 2015– )

2.plot: In this course I will share with you a technique to reach God-consciousness. Spiritual breakthrough is about God-consciousness. The goal is to reach a level of consciousness that allows us to be as aware of God as of ourselves. Imagine being as aware of God as we are of ourselves. This is the breakthrough we seek.
